            "id": 6310950,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 愛彼迎(ABNB-US)大跌5.03%，報133.02美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>愛彼迎(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ABNB:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ABNB\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ABNB-US</a>)截至台北時間15日00:43股價下跌7.05美元，報133.02美元，跌幅5.03%，成交量1,679,167（股），盤中最高價139.65美元、最低價133.02美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.57%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-1%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-1.39%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-1.39%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>愛彼迎(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ABNB:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ABNB\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ABNB-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+0.36%</li> <li>近 1 月：+7.88%</li> <li>近 3 月：+16.53%</li> <li>近 6 月：-0.04%</li> <li>今年以來：+4.14%</li></ul></section></main>",
